Eversol Hires Bank to Arrange NT$5 Billion Loan to Build Solar Wafer Plant

-- B y   Y u - H u a y   S u n
-- 
2011-02-25T09:23:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/eversol-hires-bank-to-arrange-nt-5-billion-loan-to-build-solar-wafer-plant.html
  Eversol Corp . hired First Commercial
Bank to arrange a loan of as much as NT$5 billion to help build
a solar wafer plant and boost working capital, the Taipei-based
company said in a statement to the stock exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
